      <title>戈皮纳特表示，债务高企，流动性风险令国际货币基金组织担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/liquidity-risks-are-worrying-imf-amid-high-debt-gopinath-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织二号官员表示，随着各国为疫情期间发行的债务进行再融资，国际货币基金组织正在关注潜在的市场流动性风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/liquidity-risks-are-worrying-imf-amid-high-debt-gopinath-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:04:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道富银行首席执行官：押注美联储降息毫无意义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-17/bets-on-fed-rate-cuts-make-no-sense-state-street-ceo-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道富银行董事长兼首席执行官罗恩·奥汉利表示，押注美国降息毫无意义。奥汉利在世界经济论坛上接受彭博电视台采访时表示：“我认为美联储的点阵图非常明确，我不知道为什么市场决定将其加倍，然后再采取行动。”年会在瑞士达沃斯举行。 “我认为美联储如果有什么不同的话，那就是维持利率不变。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-17/bets-on-fed-rate-cuts-make-no-sense-state-street-ceo-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场对降息“有点兴奋”：国际货币基金组织戈皮纳特</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-17/markets-a-little-exuberant-on-rate-cuts-imf</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织第一副总裁吉塔·戈皮纳特在讨论央行降息预期和全球经济状况时表示，在通胀方面“工作尚未完成”。她在瑞士达沃斯举行的世界经济论坛年会上接受彭博电视台采访时发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-17/markets-a-little-exuberant-on-rate-cuts-imf</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:00:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国提出新规则以结束高透支费打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/us-proposes-new-rule-to-end-high-overdraft-fees-in-crack-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府公布了一项期待已久的法规，该法规可能会将最大银行的透支费收入每年削减多达 35 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/us-proposes-new-rule-to-end-high-overdraft-fees-in-crack-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>邮局丑闻升级，富士通损失 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/fujitsu-takes-1-billion-knock-as-post-office-scandal-escalates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，富士通公司的欧洲首席执行官表示，该公司有道义责任为其在英国邮局丑闻中所扮演的角色提供赔偿，该公司的市值蒸发了超过 10 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/fujitsu-takes-1-billion-knock-as-post-office-scandal-escalates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 09:51:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国提高利率并引入爬行钉住汇率制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bangladesh-central-bank-raises-key-policy-rate-to-tame-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国央行提高了关键利率，并为当地货币引入了爬行钉住汇率制度，以遏制顽固的通货膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/bangladesh-central-bank-raises-key-policy-rate-to-tame-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 09:33:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>极端冰冷天气使欧洲部分地区的旅行陷入瘫痪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/extreme-icy-weather-paralyzes-travel-in-parts-of-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国和欧洲其他地区的冰冻天气威胁到大范围的公路、铁路和航班中断，因为该地区将面临降雪和厚冰堆积。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/extreme-icy-weather-paralyzes-travel-in-parts-of-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 09:04:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安哥拉表示“完全致力于”对抗通货膨胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/angola-is-totally-committed-to-fight-inflation-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安哥拉财政部长维拉·戴夫斯·德索萨表示，安哥拉央行“完全致力于”控制顽固的高通胀，政府试图增加当地产量以减少该国对进口的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/angola-is-totally-committed-to-fight-inflation-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 08:04:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
